item.title: CVE-2024-25644|2024-03-12T00:33:44.473Z -- SAP_SE -- NetWeaver (WSRM)
item.description: Under certain conditions SAP NetWeaver WSRM - version 7.50, allows an attacker to access information which would otherwise be restricted, causing low impact on Confidentiality with no impact on Integrity and Availability of the application.
